    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《<strong>回声风暴</strong>》的世界中尽可能长时间地躲避敌人的攻击！利用组合角色、武器和能力的可能性，变得更加强大。死亡会重置进度，但存活时间越长，角色获得的能力就越强。敌人的数量也在不断增加，战斗的强度也在不断提高。找到最佳能力组合，努力消灭所有敌人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282200/extras/fea92a735075695e702871aeecbd33b8.poster.avif?t=1767825023\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282200/extras/fea92a735075695e702871aeecbd33b8.webm?t=1767825023\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282200/extras/fea92a735075695e702871aeecbd33b8.mp4?t=1767825023\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索《回声风暴》的世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择更适合自己游戏风格的初始角色、武器和能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找更有效的方法消灭特定敌人并躲避他们的攻击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 5 个不同的星球上生存，面对各种凶猛的生物和环境。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >组合能力</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次提升等级时，您都会获得一种新能力。进行独特的组合，获得更强大的能力！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282200/extras/c4c8d4d1860614632fff28a09d6d7577.avif?t=1767825023\" width=598 height=292 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>也支持中文</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >升级</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁新角色、武器和能力，在《回声风暴》的世界中获得更多新的生存方式！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建设你的基地，提高角色的健康、伤害和其他属性，并获得更多资源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>现在就投入战斗吧</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282200/extras/7862357d58b12ef074e835fe40e87840.poster.avif?t=1767825023\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282200/extras/7862357d58b12ef074e835fe40e87840.webm?t=1767825023\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282200/extras/7862357d58b12ef074e835fe40e87840.mp4?t=1767825023\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
